---
title: Garlic & Herb Beef Strips with Roast Veggie Couscous, Basil Pesto & Feta
description: Quickly-cooked beef strips meld together wonderfully with nutty basil pesto in this Mediterranean-style dish. Make it a meal with fluffy couscous and crumbly feta, and now you’ve got yourself a fusion of textures and flavours you simply can’t miss out on!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pesto-beef-strips-roast-veggie-couscous-d32652aa.jpg
